+kavacha-welcome-newtab-description = Both stay out of your way. You can switch anytime in Settings.
+kavacha-welcome-newtab-floating = A centered search bar, ready to type
+kavacha-welcome-newtab-dashboard = A quiet dashboard: clock, greeting, and a daily photo
